<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Im only half way but it&apos;s very interesting, it makes us see how much society has change especially in the way the people conduct and talk to each othe<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Im only half way but it's very interesting, it makes us see how much society has change especially in the way the people conduct and talk to each other. I see that there was a movie also made from this book in 1954 might give it a try after finishing the book.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
